content: The key takeaways that we'll share with you for Q3 are record revenue of $428 million, up 17% year-over-year and up 15% year-over-year through Q3; non-GAAP operating margin, up 110 basis points year-over-year through Q3; and commitment to our plans for margin expansion in 2022 and 2023.
